      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COUSIN JOHNNY (1) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (24.34) at this track behind Blame Margaret in a Rank Limit - Restricted Win. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Capable of going well again. BIG WEEKEND (3) doesn't win out of turn but looks close to breaking through. Has been in the minors the last two runs, the latest finishing second (24.69) at this track. Has a strong record from box 3, including two wins. Expecting another good run. PAW MELODY (8) charged out of the inside draw with a fast early sectional but swamped late when a close up fourth (22.94) at Shepparton over 390m. Better than last start and can bounce back. IVORY RAMEN (6) can return to form after missing the top-three at this circuit last time out.",
